            <div class="block-content">
                <section>
                    <h2>About</h2>
                    <p class="text-main">Hi! Do you need a functional website? Because I'm a guy who makes functional websites. </p>

                    <p>I possess diverse professional experience, including:</p>
                    <ul class="text-main">
                        <li>Enterprise Software</li>
                        <li>Agency Work</li>
                        <li>Branding</li>
                        <li>UI/UX/IA</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-main">I work well with designers, content specialists, and backend developers. I am interested in tackling challenges in content management and web applications.   </p>
                    <p><a href="{{ base_url }}/about" class="btn btn-default">More About Me</a></p>
                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg">
                        <img src="{{ url('theme://images/wilkerson-suzygram.jpg') }}" alt="I have a dog. We live in Portland." class="img-responsive" />
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2>Things I <span>do</span> well</h2>
                    <p>I got my first webdev gig as a freshman in college. Here is a short list of skills learned since then.</p>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9 col-md-8">
                            <h3>Fundamentals</h3>
                            <ul class="list-inline">
                                <li>Semantic HTML,</li> <li>CSS,</li> <li>jQuery,</li> <li>OOP Principles,</li> <li>Mobile-first designing.</li> 
                            </ul>

                            <h3>Javascript Frameworks</h3>
                            <ul class="list-inline">
                                <li>Kendo UI,</li> <li>AngularJS,</li> <li>KnockoutJS.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3>Modern Technologies</h3>
                            <ul class="list-inline">
                                <li>Git,</li> <li> SASS,</li> <li> LESS,</li> <li> AJAX,</li> <li> RESTful Services,</li> <li> Task Managers,</li> <li> Twig,</li> <li> Jade,</li> <li> Handlebars...</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3>Content Management</h3>
                            <ul class="list-inline">
                                <li>Wordpress,</li> <li> GravCMS,</li> <li> CraftCMS,</li> <li> Apostrophe,</li> <li> Propietary.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <p class="quick-links"><a href='{{ page.find('/qualifications').url }}#_skills' class="btn btn-default">See More Details</a></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hidden-xs col-sm-3 col-md-4">
                            <img src="{{ url('theme://images/jeff-website-portland-guy.jpg') }}" alt="Portland Web Developer Jeff Wilkerson" class="img-responsive" alt="Originally born in St. Louis, 8 states later, I'm making my home in Portland, OR">        
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="quick-tab-btns">
                    <h2>Check It Out</h2>
                    <div class="">
                        <ul class="block-grid-sm-3">
                            <li class="block-grid-item"><a href="{{ base_url}}/qualifications" class="btn btn-default">My Skills</a></li>
                            <li class="block-grid-item"><a href="{{ base_url}}/projects" class="btn btn-default">Portfolio</a></li>
                            <li class="block-grid-item"><a href="{{ base_url}}/services" class="btn btn-default">Services</a></li>
                            <li class="block-grid-item"><a href="http://blog.jeffwilkerson.net" class="btn btn-default">My Blog</a></li>
                            <li class="block-grid-item"><a href="{{ site.social['github'].url }}" class="btn btn-default" target="_blank">Me on Github </a></li>
                            <li class="block-grid-item"><a href="{{ base_url }}/about" class="btn btn-default">More About Me</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </section>


                <section class="client-list">
                    <h2>Past Clients Include</h2>

                    <div class="xrow hidden-xs">
                        <ul class="block-grid-sm-2 block-grid-sm-4">
                            <li class="block-grid-item text-center">
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Papa Murphy's Franchising</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/papa-murphys-logo.png')}}" alt="Papa Murphy's Franchising" />
                            </li>

                            <li class="block-grid-item text-center">
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Singing Success</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/ss360-logo.png')}}" alt="Singing Success" />
                            </li>
                            <li class="block-grid-item text-center">
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Adidas, Inc.</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/adidas-logo.png')}}" alt="Adidas, Inc." />
                            </li>
                            <li class="block-grid-item text-center">
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Penske Auto Group</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/penske-auto-logo.png')}}" alt="Penske Auto Group" />
                            </li>

                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div id='client-slideshow' class='visible-xs carousel slide text-center' data-ride='carousel' data-interval="2500"> 
                        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                            <li data-target="#client-slideshow" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                            <li data-target="#client-slideshow" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                            <li data-target="#client-slideshow" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                            <li data-target="#client-slideshow" data-slide-to="3"></li>
                            <li data-target="#client-slideshow" data-slide-to="4"></li>
                            <li data-target="#client-slideshow" data-slide-to="5"></li>
                        </ol>
                        <div class='carousel-inner' role='listbox'>
                            <div class='item active'>
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Papa Murphy's Franchising</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/papa-murphys-logo.png')}}" alt="Papa Murphy's Franchising" />
                            </div>
                            <div class='item'>

                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Singing Success</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/ss360-logo.png')}}" alt="Singing Success" />
                            </div>
                            <div class='item'>
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Adidas, Inc.</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/adidas-logo.png')}}" alt="Adidas, Inc." />
                            </div>
                            <div class='item'>
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Penske Auto Group</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/penske-auto-logo.png')}}" alt="Penske Auto Group" />
                            </div>
                            <div class='item'>
                                <h4 class="title-three title-main mywhite">Dimmit Auto Group</h4>
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="{{ url('theme://images/dimmit-logo.jpg')}}" alt="Dimmit Auto Group" />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                      <!-- Controls -->
                      <a class="left carousel-control" href="#client-slideshow" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                      </a>
                      <a class="right carousel-control" href="#client-slideshow" role="button" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                      </a>
                    </div>
                </section>
                                                                        

                <section class="recent-blog-posts">
                    <h2>Blog Posts...</h2>
                    
                    <ul class='list-unstyled'>
                    {% for post in recent_blog_bosts[0:5] %}
                         <li>
                            <h4 class="blog-title">
                                <a href="{{ post.link }}" class="myred text-main">
                                    <i class='glyphicon glyphicon-menu-right'></i>
                                    {{ post.title }}
                                </a>
                            </h4>
                            <p class="blog-info">{{ post.date }} | 
                                    {% if post.tags %}
                                    Tags: 
                                        {% for tag in post.tags %} 
                                            <a href="{{ tag.link }}">{{ tag.name }}</a>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}
                                        {% endfor %}
                                    {% else %}
                                        {% if post.categories|length > 1 %}
                                            Categories:
                                        {% else %}
                                            Category: 
                                        {% endif %}
                                           {% for tag in post.categories %} 
                                            <a href="{{ tag.link }}">{{ tag.name }}</a>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}
                                        {% endfor %}
                                    {% endif %}
                                </p>
                        </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                    </ul>

                </section>


                <section>
                    <h2>Silly Instagrams...</h2>
                    <ul class="block-grid-xs-2 block-grid-sm-3">
